    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at old photos today... and i didnt even recognize the person in them. it feels like that version of me actually died a long time ago. now i'm just kind of... a ghost. just walking around in a body that doesnt belong to anyone anymore. it's exhausting pretending to be alive when the real me is long gone.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
