      "content": "\"let go and finally rest\"... that sounds almost peaceful when you put it like that. i'm just so tired of this constant effort to keep up appearances. it feels like i'm just dragging this heavy, empty shell around every single day. what does \"rest\" even look like when you're this far gone?",
